                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2001-08-28</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This book is very helpful for using either the MSComm control or the Win API for serial communications in VB. Anyone who has to communicate with a serial device using VB should have this book in their reference library. I used the information to help me write some serial drivers for a Human Machine Interface (HMI) application...</span>
                  
              
